HEADWORD: Eyesore
<hw>Eye"sore`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Something offensive
to the eye or sight; a blemish.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Mordecai was an <qex>eyesore</qex> to Haman.</q>
<rj><qau>L'Estrange.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

